<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV54">
<l>vīcuñ ciṟakāṟ paṟattīrviṇ ṇāṭunuṅ kaṭkeḷitu</l>
<l>pēcum paṭiyaṉṉa pēciyum pōvatu neytoṭuvuṇ</l>
<l>ṭēcum paṭiyaṉṉa ceyyumem mīcarviṇ ṇōrpirāṉār</l>
<l>māciṉ malaraṭik kīḻemmaic cērvikkum vaṇṭukaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You flying with flapping wings, easy for your eyes [to see] the heavenly land,</l>
<l>bees, who, even though [your] speaking is [only] like a manner of speaking,</l>
<l>[your] going will make us join under the flawless flower feet of the lord of celestials,</l>
<l>our lord, who, in digging into [and] eating the butter acted thus in a manner they reproached.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
